{"tid":2387850,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"攪和GameSpot大戰？臉書下架熱門股票討論社團","createTime":"2021-01-30T15:51:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-30T16:04:50.000Z","uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8eda7cdbf3c60013b5ff70aa01eb258549209b7d","tid":2387850,"uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T15:51:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/business/page/800/2021/01/29/phpbcFDuo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fbusiness%2Fpage%2F800%2F2021%2F01%2F29%2FphpbcFDuo.jpg&h=56e95c45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美遊戲零售商GameStop史詩級軋空戰引發國際關注，就連美國會也介入關心，尤其在網路券商「羅賓漢」（Robinhood）突宣布有限制用戶購買該檔股票後引爆鄉民怒火，現在就連臉書也加入戰場，封殺平台上頗受歡迎的股市討論社團「羅賓漢股票交易員」（Robinhood Stock Traders）。<br />\n<br />\n《路透》報導，該群組有約15.7萬名成員，在同類型的社團中頗具規模。23歲的創辦人特蘭（Allen Tran）表示，他於當地時間週三收到臉書的下架通知，且沒有提供任何細節，僅說該社團觸犯了「成人性剝削」政策，但他強調從未在自己的社團內看到成人內容。<br />\n<br />\n特蘭批評，「對於那些看到散戶取得成功就感到失落的大型機構，他們會試著鎖定任何可行的目標。」臉書證實封鎖該社團，但無進一步評論。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3425839\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3425839&d=auZED%2BZQxHi6416lNwsUjGWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=2df10843\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3425839&h=25aaa883\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3425839</a>"},{"pid":"160443db603926304160745b06469f2746fbcfe9","tid":2387850,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T15:53:14.000Z","msg":"deep state<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/vampire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22a046ed97547f08ce59afb04db573097233895c","tid":2387850,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T15:54:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 